Curation Notes: 8 August 2008 Taxon list compiled by CRM & Leah Mabee - present in pub (12 pages)
16 Sept 2008: Jeff Engeman Taxon list and matrix merged. Matrix based on publication Tables 6 through 8 (pages 199-202). Publication matrix taxa (40 taxa) was mostly by family and based on hypotheses presented in the paper--not the same family groupings as in the taxon list. Expanded matrix (314 taxa) based on arguements from the publication as to which genera belonged to which family. Documented in Taxon Comments.
Some taxa do not have the correct Catalog ID. This needs to be reviewed. JGL has reviewed and corrected taxon misspellings and requested via the TTO tracker the several additional taxon names needed for Mo 1991 September 21, 2008.
Checked for polymorphs in Table 3-4. There were none. AB 10/18/12

incomplete loop and the element which represents the mesocoracoid becomes slender bar with a free upper end

more or less superior and moderately developed eyes
eyes reduced and bear no free rims
